entries.femaleVariant: This... I-I can't believe this. You were supposed to protect her!
How could you let this happen? How, you dumb bitch?!
entries.maleVariant: How could you let this happen? How, you dumb fuck?!

entries.femaleVariant: Watch your tone.
I'm sorry.
I don't like your tone. Better watch it.
I-I'm sorry. The... the foot traffic, I...
entries.maleVariant: I-I'm sorry. The foot traffic, I...

entries.femaleVariant: You weren't supposed to kill anyone, but... Ugh... Maybe it's for the best.
Listen... I'll hang back and make sure nobody spills to the media vultures. Oh, and your fee, of course. I'll transfer it the second I get home. Promise!
Agreed.
Oh my God, V... Thank you, thank you so much!
Girl like that... Who'd have thought? What... what do we do now?
Wait till the badges get here.
This.
But... What about when they let her out? Or... or she escapes?
Then you give me another call.
Holy shit, V! What the fuck?! Have you lost your mind?!
Go! Before I do something I'll regret.
Oh, I'll watch... As you choke on your own blood!
Go! Go fucking drown yourself!
No rush. See ya later, Blue Moon. And watch your back.
Don't mention it. It's what I was paid to do.
Me? No. But no question that she did. If we gave her up to the police, eventually she'd've walked free. Or escaped.
And whaddaya think she'd do then? Who'd she go visit?
OK... You're right. I... Thank you for everything. I'll transfer your eddies soon. Promise!
Go get a stiff drink, cool your nerves. Take care, Blue Moon.
How... How'd you know it was her?
Maybe we'd better leave it to the badges.
She was actin' weird... turned out she was also packin' iron and pictures of you... With your eyes cut out.
Pretty solid evidence, wouldn't you say?
Blue Moon? I've got her.
Did you say "her?" Hm, well, there's a twist. I'm headin' there right now.
V, think what you're doing!
The police can handle her!
We're in public!
